## Boundary

This trace validates the current local/dev ASP.NET Core Minimal API host skeleton only.

Program.cs maps the Minimal API host.
MapAdventuresAuthEndpoints maps the /auth endpoint group.
AdventuresAuthEndpointHandlers are thin transport handlers.
IAdventuresAuthApiService owns API DTO translation.
IAdventuresAuthDecisionService / AdventuresAuthDecisionService owns auth decisions.

No production deployment was used.
No OAuth/OpenID behavior was used.
No RBAC, tenant, or organization model was used.
No persistence/database behavior was used.
No real password storage was used.
No external identity provider was used.
No BlogEngine.NET dependency was introduced.
No Blazor UI was added.

